                            <comment id="14453905" author="brettporter" created="Tue, 4 Sep 2007 07:48:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;check in 2.3.1 as well, if it works there then move to 2.4.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14453948" author="jason.greene@redhat.com" created="Thu, 6 Sep 2007 20:04:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It appears to work on 2.3.1-SNAPSHOT but not 2.4-SNAPSHOT&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14453937" author="jason.greene@redhat.com" created="Mon, 1 Oct 2007 11:04:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Strike that. The 2.3.X does not work on all platforms. I am seeing failures in Windows.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
