&lt;p&gt;Worked for me using 2.4-20071116.171416-14&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Doesn&apos;t work anymore with the latest SNAPSHOT.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14453979" author="dfabulich" created="Fri, 23 Nov 2007 21:09:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&quot;mvn test -Dmaven.test.redirectTestOutputToFile=true&quot; seems to do the right thing (and doesn&apos;t truncate the summary) for me right now with the 2.4 trunk.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
